[
    {
        "text": "Seventy-one years ago, on a bright cloudless morning,...",
        "startTime": 1289,
        "endTime": 8113,
        "slowStartTime": 2084,
        "slowEndTime": 12394
    },
    {
        "text": "...death fell from the sky and the world was changed.",
        "startTime": 10374,
        "endTime": 14225,
        "slowStartTime": 15711,
        "slowEndTime": 21562
    },
    {
        "text": "A flash of light and a wall of fire destroyed a city...",
        "startTime": 16867,
        "endTime": 22761,
        "slowStartTime": 25451,
        "slowEndTime": 34366
    },
    {
        "text": "...and demonstrated that mankind possessed the means to destroy itself.",
        "startTime": 24806,
        "endTime": 31071,
        "slowStartTime": 37359,
        "slowEndTime": 46832
    },
    {
        "text": "Why do we come to this place, to Hiroshima?",
        "startTime": 35553,
        "endTime": 40271,
        "slowStartTime": 53479,
        "slowEndTime": 60631
    },
    {
        "text": "We come to ponder a terrible force unleashed in a not-so-distant past.",
        "startTime": 42942,
        "endTime": 49704,
        "slowStartTime": 64563,
        "slowEndTime": 74781
    },
    {
        "text": "We come to mourn the dead,...",
        "startTime": 53007,
        "endTime": 54257,
        "slowStartTime": 79661,
        "slowEndTime": 81611
    },
    {
        "text": "...including over 100,000 Japanese men, women and children,...",
        "startTime": 55901,
        "endTime": 61733,
        "slowStartTime": 84002,
        "slowEndTime": 92825
    },
    {
        "text": "...thousands of Koreans, a dozen Americans held prisoner.",
        "startTime": 63860,
        "endTime": 70002,
        "slowStartTime": 95940,
        "slowEndTime": 105228
    },
    {
        "text": "Their souls speak to us.",
        "startTime": 74547,
        "endTime": 76417,
        "slowStartTime": 111971,
        "slowEndTime": 114851
    },
    {
        "text": "They ask us to look inward,...",
        "startTime": 78778,
        "endTime": 80581,
        "slowStartTime": 118317,
        "slowEndTime": 121096
    },
    {
        "text": "...to take stock of who we are and what we might become.",
        "startTime": 82331,
        "endTime": 87421,
        "slowStartTime": 123647,
        "slowEndTime": 131356
    },
    {
        "text": "Those who died, they are like us.",
        "startTime": 91535,
        "endTime": 95510,
        "slowStartTime": 137452,
        "slowEndTime": 143490
    },
    {
        "text": "Ordinary people understand this, I think.",
        "startTime": 101523,
        "endTime": 103619,
        "slowStartTime": 152435,
        "slowEndTime": 155653
    },
    {
        "text": "They do not want more war.",
        "startTime": 106223,
        "endTime": 108489,
        "slowStartTime": 159485,
        "slowEndTime": 162958
    },
    {
        "text": "They would rather that the wonders of science be focused on improving life...",
        "startTime": 110574,
        "endTime": 116963,
        "slowStartTime": 166011,
        "slowEndTime": 175670
    },
    {
        "text": "...and not eliminating it.",
        "startTime": 117917,
        "endTime": 119230,
        "slowStartTime": 177026,
        "slowEndTime": 179070
    },
    {
        "text": "When the choices made by nations,...",
        "startTime": 122697,
        "endTime": 124505,
        "slowStartTime": 184196,
        "slowEndTime": 186982
    },
    {
        "text": "...when the choices made by leaders reflect this simple wisdom,...",
        "startTime": 125197,
        "endTime": 130967,
        "slowStartTime": 187945,
        "slowEndTime": 196676
    },
    {
        "text": "...then the lesson of Hiroshima is done.",
        "startTime": 133232,
        "endTime": 135906,
        "slowStartTime": 199998,
        "slowEndTime": 204084
    }
]